  "subtitle": "Freedom to stream — unofficial AltStore-compatible source for iOS / iPadOS.",
  "description": "An unofficial AltStore source for Stremio iOS / iPadOS, compatible with any signing app that consumes the standard AltStore source format (Feather, AltStore Classic, AltStore PAL, ESign, Scarlet, Sideloadly, and others). Stremio's official source at dl.strem.io/apple/altstore/source.json cannot be parsed by most signing apps because it uses Apple's encrypted App Store Connect marketplace manifest format; this source points to plain IPA artifacts publicly available on the dl.strem.io CDN. Includes two packages: Stremio PAL (full-featured, com.stremio.pal) and Stremio Lite (legacy, com.stremio.ios). For Apple TV (tvOS) add the separate source: stremio-tvos.json. This is an unofficial community port, not supported by Stremio.",
